## 6. Insights Engine

### 6.1 Post-Transaction Insights (Synchronous)

**Low stock alert** — triggered immediately after `update_stock_level`:

```typescript
// src/lib/insights/lowStock.ts

export async function checkLowStockInsights(
  db: SupabaseClient,
  businessId: string,
  items: TransactionItem[]
) {
  for (const item of items) {
    const { data: stockLevel } = await db
      .from('stock_levels')
      .select('quantity, product_variants(reorder_threshold, products(name))')
      .eq('variant_id', item.matched_variant_id || item.variant_id)
      .single();

    if (stockLevel && stockLevel.quantity <= stockLevel.product_variants.reorder_threshold) {
      // Check if alert already exists (avoid duplicates)
      const { data: existing } = await db
        .from('insights_log')
        .select('id')
        .eq('business_id', businessId)
        .eq('type', 'low_stock')
        .eq('related_variant_id', item.matched_variant_id)
        .eq('is_read', false)
        .single();

      if (!existing) {
        await db.from('insights_log').insert({
          business_id: businessId,
          type: 'low_stock',
          title: `Low Stock: ${stockLevel.product_variants.products.name}`,
          message: `Only ${stockLevel.quantity} units remaining (threshold: ${stockLevel.product_variants.reorder_threshold})`,
          severity: stockLevel.quantity === 0 ? 'critical' : 'warning',
          related_variant_id: item.matched_variant_id,
        });

        // Push to chat as system message
        await db.from('chat_messages').insert({
          business_id: businessId,
          user_id: '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000', // system user
          role: 'system',
          content: `⚠️ Low Stock Alert: ${stockLevel.product_variants.products.name} is down to ${stockLevel.quantity} units.`,
          metadata: { type: 'insight', insight_type: 'low_stock' },
        });
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### 6.2 Nightly Batch Insights (Cron)

```typescript
// src/app/api/cron/insights/route.ts

export async function POST(req: Request) {
  // Auth: verify cron secret
  if (req.headers.get('Authorization') !== `Bearer ${process.env.CRON_SECRET}`) {
    return Response.json({ error: 'Unauthorized' }, { status: 401 });
  }

  const db = createServiceRoleClient();

  // Get all active businesses
  const { data: businesses } = await db.from('businesses').select('id');

  for (const biz of businesses || []) {
    await evaluateReorderSuggestions(db, biz.id);
    await evaluateSlowMovers(db, biz.id);
    await evaluateExpiryWarnings(db, biz.id);
    await evaluateRevenueMilestones(db, biz.id);

    // Weekly only (run on Sundays)
    if (new Date().getDay() === 0) {
      await evaluateTopPerformers(db, biz.id);
    }
  }

  return Response.json({ success: true });
}
```

### 6.3 Insight Evaluator Details

| Type | Logic | SQL Core |
|------|-------|----------|
| **Reorder suggestion** | 14-day avg daily sales × 7 > current stock | `SELECT variant_id, SUM(quantity)/14.0 AS daily_rate FROM transaction_items ti JOIN transactions t ON ti.transaction_id=t.id WHERE t.type='sale' AND t.created_at > NOW()-INTERVAL '14 days' GROUP BY variant_id HAVING SUM(quantity)/14.0 * 7 > (SELECT quantity FROM stock_levels WHERE variant_id=ti.variant_id)` |
| **Slow mover** | No sales in 21 days + qty > 10 | `SELECT pv.id FROM product_variants pv JOIN stock_levels sl ON pv.id=sl.variant_id WHERE sl.quantity > 10 AND pv.id NOT IN (SELECT variant_id FROM transaction_items ti JOIN transactions t ON ti.transaction_id=t.id WHERE t.type='sale' AND t.created_at > NOW()-INTERVAL '21 days')` |
| **Expiry warning** | expiry_date within 14 days | `SELECT * FROM product_variants WHERE expiry_date IS NOT NULL AND expiry_date <= NOW() + INTERVAL '14 days' AND expiry_date > NOW()` |
| **Revenue milestone** | This week revenue ≥ 1.2 × last week revenue | Compare `SUM(total_amount)` for current vs previous 7-day windows |
| **Top performer** | Top 5 by revenue this week | `SELECT product_name, SUM(total_price) FROM transaction_items ti JOIN transactions t GROUP BY product_name ORDER BY SUM(total_price) DESC LIMIT 5` |

### 6.4 Pushing Insights to Chat

When an insight is created in `insights_log`, a corresponding row is inserted into `chat_messages` with `role: 'system'`. Because `chat_messages` has Realtime enabled (migration 003), all connected clients receive the new message via their Supabase subscription.

Chat UI renders system messages differently:
- **Low stock / Expiry**: amber background, warning icon
- **Revenue milestone / Top performer**: teal/green background, trending-up icon
- **Reorder / Slow mover**: blue background, info icon

### 6.5 Environment Variables for Insights

```env
CRON_SECRET=your-random-secret-string-here
```

Add to `vercel.json`:

```json
{
  "crons": [
    {
      "path": "/api/cron/insights",
      "schedule": "0 2 * * *"
    }
  ]
}
```
